In Sprint 1 B: Add Spring Cloud Gateway dependency in the Mithril Gateway project, you need to perform the following steps:

Open the build configuration file (pom.xml) in the project.
Add the Spring Cloud Gateway dependency to the file.
Save the changes to the file.
Build the project to ensure that the dependency was added successfully.
Here's an example of how to add the Spring Cloud Gateway dependency to the pom.xml file:

php
Copy code
<dependency>
    <groupId>org.springframework.cloud</groupId>
    <artifactId>spring-cloud-starter-gateway</artifactId>
    <version>3.0.0</version>
</dependency>

After adding the dependency, you can proceed to configure and use the Spring Cloud Gateway in the project.
